      "config": {
        "text": "In this example we want to show how to implement a simple agent for skills testing\nThe logic is as follows:\n1) The user answers questions on a topic you define\n2) The agent evaluates the answer and increases or decreases the score\n3) Once the score exceeds 10, the agent's work is considered complete\n\nThis is an example of a stateful agent that maintains state between calls."
